      <title>模电</title>
      <link href="/2024/06/21/%E6%A8%A1%E7%94%B5/"/>
      <url>/2024/06/21/%E6%A8%A1%E7%94%B5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h1 id="二极管"><a href="#二极管" class="headerlink" title="二极管"></a>二极管</h1><p>单向导电性</p><h4 id="伏安特性："><a href="#伏安特性：" class="headerlink" title="伏安特性："></a>伏安特性：</h4><p><img src="https://github.com/Armke/Armke.github.io/blob/main/img/modian/%E4%BA%8C%E6%9E%81%E7%AE%A1%E4%BC%8F%E5%AE%89%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7.png?raw=true"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
